# Intuition
$conver[i] = nums[i] + \displaystyle\max_{0 \le j \le i} (nums[j])$
$score(nums) = \sum conver(nums)$

$ans[i] = score(nums[0...i])$
$ans[i] = \sum conver(nums[0...i])$

$ans[i]$ is the the prefix sum of $conver[i]$

$ans[i] = \left(\displaystyle\sum conver(nums[0...i-1])\right) + conver[i]$
$ans[i] = ans[i - 1] + conver[i]$
$ans[i] = ans[i - 1] + nums[i] + \displaystyle\max_{0 \le j \le i} (nums[j])$

# Approach
Maintain $maximum$ value till current index.
$ans[i] = ans[i - 1] + nums[i] + maximum$



