# Approach
Iterate the initial array. Store both max so far and score of i-1. For ith element max(i) = max(max(i-1), nums(i)), score(i) = score(i-1) + max(i) + nums(i).

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(N)

- Space complexity:
O(1)

