# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Hello guys, Here you just have to simply iterate the array and keep a max count  till  ith index.


# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
 Here I am explaining my approach :
1.) Simply iterate the array from 1st index to last.
2.) Keep a max to keep account of maximum till the ith index. 
3.) Simply add this max to current index to get the value.
4.) Now you have sum the elements of this ans array to get final result.
