<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Simple Observation. `ans` store cummulative sum of elements of `conver` of whole `nums`.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Rather than calculating `conver` for whole `nums`, As we want to store cummulative sum as we iterate through `conver` in `ans`.
`conver[i] = nums[i] + maxi`, so rather than storing `conver`,
take a variable `sum` we stores cummulative sum of elements of `conver` on each iteration, and store the value in the corresponding `ans[i]`.


