# Intuition
For solving thing problem we are going to use closure concept. As we go through the problem, two thing is sure ->

We need to store starting init value in variable because when we implement reset function we need them that value.

And also store current value, which will change when we call increment or decrement or reset function.

# Approach
1. We are going to create two variable which will store init value and current value.
2. After that we will create three function increment, decrement, rest.
3. return these function.

# Complexity
