Answer is possible when nodecount*nodecount-1 == edgecount in a connected component.

To visualise this you can easily take a complete graph of nodesize 3 and 4 and varify it manually.

# Approach

simple finding connected component with finding nodecount and edgecount. then verify and increase the answer

