# Approach
Create the graph using adjacency matrix. Iterate thru all the vertices and check if visited or not. If not visited then perform bfs on that vertex and count the number of edges and nodes in the component. For the component to be connected nodes * (nodes - 1) == edges. If this case is true then update the result by 1. Return the result after all the vertices are explored.


