# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Find out the no. of nodes and the no. of edges in all the components.
If in a component, edges >= nodes*(nodes-1), it is a complete connected component.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Use DFS to keep track of no. of edges and nodes in every component.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(V + E)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: O(V)
