# **Explanation**
Check if `s[i] == s[i - 1]`.
If they are different, we need to either:
1. change the prefix to from start to `s[i - 1]`, cost `i`.
2. change the suffix from `s[i]` to end, cost `n - i`.
<br>

# **Complexity**
Time `O(n)`
Space `O(1)`
<br>

