# APPROACH 1: 

**ALGO:**

* basically hame saare char equal krne h

* i=1 se shuru karo aur har s[i] ko s[i-1] se compare karo

* agar ye dono equal h : to iska mtlb ye h ki index 0 se i tk sabhi elements equal h(kyuinki ye procedure ham shuru se krte aa rhe h)

* aur agar unequal h to mtlb:

					0 se i-1 tk to sab equal h because ye procedure ham shuru se krte aa rhe h
					but index i-1 aur i pr values different h

					=> ya to 0 se lekar i-1 tk inversion perform kr do taaki sab i k equal ho jae  (mtlb cost = i ko ans me add kr do)

					=> ya fir i se lekar n-1 tk inversion perform kr do taaki sab i-1 k equal ho jae  (mtlb cost = n-i ko ans me add kr do)

					=>in dono me se jo kam wali cost h us hisab se operation perform karo (GREEDY)



**CODE :**

