# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We do 1st operation on the first half of the string and second operation for the second half of the string,for both having all 0s and all 1s and the operation is sum with first half and second half,and take minimum of converting to 0s and converting to 1s

# Complexity
